pma:database.name: qms change requests
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `employee_details` ( `ID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Emp_Id` text NOT NULL, `Emp_Password` text NOT NULL, `Name` text NOT NULL, `Designation` text NOT NULL, `Email_Id` text NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`ID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=119 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `qms cr table` ( `ID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `RequestType` text NOT NULL, `ChangeRequestID` text NOT NULL, `Requestor` text NOT NULL, `RequestedFilePath` text NOT NULL, `CRDescription` text NOT NULL, `ImpactedFiles` text NOT NULL, `RequestedDate` text NOT NULL, `CCB Status` text NOT NULL, `CCB Remarks` text NOT NULL, `SME Approver` text NOT NULL, `Quality Approver` text NOT NULL, `Other Approvers` text NOT NULL, `CRStatus` text NOT NULL, `InitialDocVersion` text NOT NULL, `Impacted Files Version` text NOT NULL, `NewDocID` text NOT NULL, `RejectReason` text NOT NULL, `Reviewer` text NOT NULL, `Review Completion Date` text NOT NULL, `Approver` text NOT NULL, `Document Approval Date` text NOT NULL, `FinalDocVersion` text NOT NULL, `Impacted Files Final Version` text NOT NULL, `CR Closed Date` text NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`ID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=5 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
